
--------------------OBJECTS------------------------------
GENERAL:
    Properties:
        -Captains
    Methods:
        -run() - should activate all Creep generation in rooms

CAPTAIN:
    Properties:
        -rooms(Screeps object)
        -ConstructionSites
        -energySources
        -totalAvailableEnergy
        -controller
        -roomToAttack
        -callingForReinforcements
        -isUnderAttack
        -safeModeAvailable
        -creepBalance - how to determine?
        -roomLevel
            -Should change based on controller level or potential energy available

    Methods:
        -activateSafeMode()
        -callForReinforcements()
        -generateScreeps()
            -Should determine how many of each type to create
        -attackRoom()
        -DefendRoom()

CREEP:
    Properties:
        -Name
        -Role
        -isWorking
        -CurrentRoom
        -TargetRoom
    
    Methods:
        -harvest()
        -upgrade()
        -build()
        -Repair()
            -Should be able to specify whether walls/ramparts are included
        -Attack()
        -Defend()

        Sub-Objects:
        -CreepHarvester
        -CreepUpgrader
        -CreepBuilder
        -CreepRepairman
        -CreepWallRepairman
        -CreepGuardian
        -CreepRaider
        -CreepDiplomat
        -CreepScout

























